values: 胸部；胸膛；柜子；金库；财箱；（用于存放物品的，常为木制的）大箱；上身（指人体从腰部到颈部的部分）
用胸部推（或顶）；用胸膛抵挡

pos_mean_info_list.mean: 胸部丰满的；胸部大的；骄傲的

word_mean_info__list.difference: 指人或动物的胸部或胸部的前面，也指男人或女人的乳房。
文学用词，与breast同义，特指女性的乳房，也可用作比喻。
指胸膛，即肋骨所包围的部分。

word_group.brief_definition: 胸围；胸廓测量；胸围尺寸
胸部伤口；胸部创伤；胸部外伤

bilingual.source: This develops your chest and shoulder muscles.
bilingual.target: 这可以锻炼你的胸部和肩部肌肉。

bilingual.source: He has a tattoo on his chest.
She covered her chest with her hands.
He crossed his arms over his chest.

bilingual.target: 漏斗胸是一种胸部畸形。

bilingual.source: She wore a necklace that hung down to her chest.
bilingual.target: 她戴了一条垂到胸部的项链。

bilingual.source: The doctor listened to his chest with a stethoscope.
bilingual.target: 医生用听诊器听他的胸部。

bilingual.source: When angina strikes, he feels severe chest pain.
bilingual.target: 绞痛发作时，他感到胸部剧烈疼痛。

yingyinNormal.en: All right, what about the third guy? You mean the guy who kept staring at your chest? Can you blame him?
yingyinNormal.zh: 第三个呢？他一直瞪着你的胸部看你能怪他吗？

yingyinNormal.en: Ooh, what a shame. Because with her face and her chest I could really put something together.
yingyinNormal.zh: 真可惜，她的脸蛋加上她的胸部，我可以捧出个明星来。

yingyinNormal.en: You should expect an increase in body hair, especially on your face, chest, armpits.
yingyinNormal.zh: 这一时期，身体会出现毛发的增长，尤其在脸部，胸部，腋窝。

yingyinNormal.en: Here. Put some hair on your chest.
yingyinNormal.zh: 给，来点更疯狂的。

yingyinNormal.en: Oh, my god! A treasure chest! I'm rich!
yingyinNormal.zh: 天呐，一个财宝箱！我发财了！

yingyinNormal.en: He said, "Please get your knee off my chest."
yingyinNormal.zh: 他说: 你请你不要用膝盖压着我的胸。

yingyinNormal.en: I've got a treasure chest. It's a biscuit tin. It's a treasure chest. But it's still got biscuits in.
yingyinNormal.zh: 我有一个宝藏箱。这是饼干铁盒。这是宝藏箱。但是这个还有饼干在里面。

yingyinNormal.en: You want to rub something on my chest? Yes. All over it.
yingyinNormal.zh: 你要帮我在胸口擦东西？是啊，整个胸口都得擦。

yingyinNormal.en: So, come on, pal. Anything you wanna get off your chest?
yingyinNormal.zh: 来吧，老兄，想说什么就说吧。

yingyinNormal.en: Wow, that feels so good to get off my chest. Okay, you go.
yingyinNormal.zh: 哇，说出来的感觉真好，好，该你了。

yingyinNormal.en: My arm, my chest, his call. His call will be to the police.
yingyinNormal.zh: 签我的手臂，我的胸膛，看他的意思吧。他只会有叫警察的意思。

yingyinNormal.en: What's your status? My chest hurts. I have broken my ribs. How are you?
yingyinNormal.zh: 你状况如何？我胸口好疼，可能肋骨断了，你怎么样？

yingyinNormal.en: So. Pop quiz. Mr. Weatherly complains of chest pain and shortness of breath.
yingyinNormal.zh: 突击考试，威瑟利先生称自己胸口疼痛，呼吸急促。

yingyinNormal.en: You want me to wrap it? No, it's okay. I'm gonna stab my friend in the chest.
yingyinNormal.zh: 要包起来吗？不用了，我要用它直刺我朋友胸口。

yingyinNormal.en: He puts three slugs into my chest. Thank God for body armor. Even I thought I was dead.
yingyinNormal.zh: 他朝我胸口开了三枪，多亏我穿了防弹衣，当时我都以为自己死了。

yingyinNormal.en: I still have to put a cold rag on your head, sing to you and apply VapoRub to your chest.
yingyinNormal.zh: 我还得在你额头放一块冷毛巾，唱歌给你听，帮你在胸口擦伤风膏。

yingyinNormal.en: Who wants a biscuit? Me. Now, it's a treasure chest. Let's find some treasure to put in it.
yingyinNormal.zh: 谁想要一块饼干？我。现在，它是个宝藏箱了。我们找一些宝藏放进去吧。

yingyinNormal.en: What treasure chest? The one we buried in the garden. Pedro's glasses are buried in the garden.
yingyinNormal.zh: 什么宝箱？我们埋在花园的那个。佩德罗的眼镜被埋在花园了。

yingyinNormal.en: Peppa and Suzy love playing doctors and nurses. So does George. Peppa listens to George's chest.
yingyinNormal.zh: 佩琪和苏西喜欢扮演医生和护士。乔治也喜欢。佩琪听了听乔治的心脏。

yingyinNormal.en: Puncture wounds to the chest and what looks like a distal radius fracture. P.85 palp, pressure 135.
yingyinNormal.zh: 胸口有刺伤，而且貌似有桡骨远端骨折血压85 ，压强135B。

direction_info.description:
数据源自2012-2023年12年间全国考研试卷，由搜狗翻译进行大数据分析汇总，数据仅供参考。

<highlight> 考频分布</highlight>
由搜狗翻译收集历年真题试卷、汇总单词出现的总频次、释义分布。题型选自2012-2023年全国考研英语一和考研英语二共24套考研试卷，包括阅读、完型填空、翻译、写作等所有题型。

<highlight> 考纲释义</highlight>
精选全国考研考纲词汇、单词义项，由搜狗大数据与考纲、历年真题进行匹配。

<highlight>真题例句</highlight>
精选2012-2023年12年间全国考研英语一和考研英语二试卷，由搜狗大数据与搜索内容匹配历年真题例句。

搜狗翻译拥有最终解释权。

examination_example.sentence: Stay alert to serious symptoms, such as <highlight>chest</highlight> pain, severe shortness of breath or dizziness, or faintness, and seek medical attention immediately.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 对严重症状保持警惕，如胸痛、严重气短、头晕或昏厥，并立即就医。

disambiguation_list.sense_disambiguation: 泛指人或动物的胸或胸腔，还可指衣服的上身前部。
指双肩到腹部胸骨所包住的范围，即前胸，尤指女性乳房。
指人的整个胸部；还可指人们感觉愉快或悲伤的源泉所在，表示“内心”、“心绪”等，多用于委婉的文学用语。
多指妇女的胸脯(乳房),通常用于女性穿上紧身上衣或选美时的胸脯部侧影。
